'''Yugurtn''' iga yan ugllid amaziɣ n [[Numidya]]. Yumẓ adɣar n babas [[Misipsa]] lliɣ immut ɣ -118, ntta d aytmas [[Hiyampsal]] d [[Ɛazarbaɛl]]. Lliɣ immut [[Ɛazarbaɛl]], ibda [[Aqryan ayugurtin|uqryan ayugurtin]] ngr ṛuma d Numidya. Ɣ usmmud n uqryan ad ittyumẓ Yugurtn ɣ -105. Iɣama ɣ ṛuma aylliɣ immut.

